.title Instrumentation Amplifier
Vcc vcc 0 15
Vee vee 0 -15
Vcm vcm 0 2.5
Vdp inp vcm 5m
Vdn vcm inn 5m
Ea1 out_a1 0 inp fb_a1 1000000
Rg1 fb_a1 mid 10k
R1a fb_a1 out_a1 24.7k
Ea2 out_a2 0 inn fb_a2 1000000
Rg2 mid fb_a2 10k
R2a fb_a2 out_a2 24.7k
R3 out_a1 diff_m 10k
R4 diff_m vout 10k
R5 out_a2 diff_p 10k
R6 diff_p 0 10k
Ea3 vout 0 diff_p diff_m 1000000
.end
